Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta ce dubban 'yan bindigan da ke yaki da Pakistan a Afghanistan
ISLAMABAD - Wani rahoto na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya ce sama da 'yan ta' addan Pakistan 6,000 ne ke buya a Afghanistan, galibinsu na kungiyar Taliban ta Pakistan ne da ke da alhakin kai hare-hare kan sojojin Pakistan da kuma fararen hular da ke kai hare-hare.
A wani rahoto da ta fitar a wannan makon ta ce kungiyar da ake kira Tehreek-e-Taliban (TTP) na da alaka da kungiyar da ke da alaka da kungiyar ISIS ta Afghanistan.
Wasu daga cikin 'ya' yan kungiyar ta TTP ma sun shiga cikin kungiyar da ke da alaka da kungiyar ta IS wacce ke da hedikwatarta a gabashin Afghanistan.
Gwamnatin Afghanistan ba ta mayar da martani ba a ranar Lahadi kan bukatar da kamfanin dillancin labarai na Associated Press ya gabatar mata na neman karin bayani.
Rahoton ya ce kungiyar IS da ke Afghanistan wacce ake kira IS a lardin Khorasan, ta sha da kyar a hannun jami 'an tsaron Afghanistan da kuma sojojin Amurka da na NATO, har ma a wani lokaci da kungiyar Taliban ta Afghanistan ta ke kai hare-hare.
Tawagar masu sa ido kan tantance bayanai da takunkumi ta Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, wacce ke bin diddigin kungiyoyin 'yan ta' adda a duniya ce ta shirya rahoton.
Rahoton ya kiyasta cewa 'ya' yan kungiyar IS a Afghanistan sun kai 2,200, kuma duk da cewa shugabancinta ya samu nakasu, har yanzu kungiyar IS na kirga cikin shugabanninta a matsayin dan asalin kasar Syria Abu Said Mohammad al-Khorasani.
Rahoton ya kuma ce tawagar masu sa ido ta samu bayanan cewa wasu manyan kwamandojin kungiyar ISIS guda biyu, Abu Qutaibah da Abu Hajar al-Iraqi, sun isa Afghanistan daga gabas ta tsakiya a kwanan nan.
"Duk da cewa a cikin yankunan da ke ja da baya, (kungiyar ISIS) ta kasance tana iya kai hare-hare masu yawa a sassa daban-daban na kasar, ciki har da Kabul.
Hakan kuma na nufin jan hankalin mayakan Taliban da ke adawa da yarjejeniyar da aka kulla da Amurka ", a cewar rahoton, yana mai nuni ne da wata yarjejeniyar zaman lafiya da Amurka ta sanya wa hannu da kungiyar Taliban a watan Fabarairu.
An kulla wannan yarjejeniyar ne domin ta ba Amurka damar kawo karshen shigar da ta ke yi a Afghanistan na tsawon shekaru 19, ta kuma yi kira ga kungiyar Taliban da ta tabbatar da cewa kasarta ba za ta yi amfani da ita daga kungiyoyin 'yan ta' adda ba.
Ana kuma sa ran yarjejeniyar za ta tabbatar da cewa 'yan Taliban duk sun shiga cikin yakin da suke yi da kungiyar IS.
Wani bangare na biyu kuma mai matukar muhimmanci a yarjejeniyar ya yi kira da a tattauna tsakanin 'yan Taliban da kuma shugabanin siyasar Kabul.
A ranar Asabar din da ta wuce, Ma 'aikatar Harkokin Wajen Amurka ta fitar da wata sanarwa tana mai cewa wakilinta na wanzar da zaman lafiya Zalmay Khalilzad ya sake yin jigila a yankin yana mai neman ya tsallake rijiya da baya a wannan tattaunawar, wacce aka rika dakatad da ita yayin da bangarorin biyu suka yi kunnen uwar shegu da shirin sakin fursunonin.
Yarjejeniyar da ke samun goyon bayan Amurka ta yi kira ga gwamnatin Afghanistan da ta saki fursunonin Taliban 5,000 da kuma 'yan Taliban da su' yantar da jami 'an gwamnati da na soji 1,000 a matsayin wata alama da ta kira mai kyau gabanin tattaunawa.
Har ya zuwa yanzu gwamnati ta ki sakin fursunonin Taliban kusan 600 da ta kira masu aikata manyan laifuka, ta kuma yi tayin samar da wasu hanyoyi kyauta.
Kungiyar Taliban dai ta ki amincewa da hakan.
"Bangarorin sun fi kusa da fara tattaunawar intra da Afghanistan, wannan shine mataki na gaba da zai kawo karshen yakin da Afghanistan ta shafe shekaru 40 tana gwabzawa", a cewar sanarwar da ma 'aikatar harkokin wajen Amurka ta fitar.
"Duk da cewa an samu gagarumin ci gaba kan musayar fursunonin, amma batun na bukatar a kara kaimi wajen warware matsalar".
Mai magana da yawun kungiyar Taliban a siyasance a farkon makon nan ya ce a shirye ta ke ta tattauna da shugabannin siyasar Kabul bayan hutun idin Layya na idin Layya a karshen watan nan, idan har aka kammala sakin fursunonin.
Wani babban abin damuwa ga kasar Pakistan shi ne kasancewar kasar Afghanistan a hannun 'yan bindiga, musamman wadanda suke da alaka da kungiyar TTP ko Jamaat-ul-Ahrar ko Lashkar-e-Islam, da kuma wadanda suke tare da kungiyar Baluchistan Liberation Army wacce ta dauki alhakin kai hare-hare masu yawa a wannan watan a lardin Sindh na kudancin kasar da kuma kudu maso yammacin lardin Baluchistan.
An kashe sojojin Pakistan da yawa a wannan watan a kudu maso yammacin lardin Baluchistan a fafatawar da suka yi da 'yan ta' addan.
